sec.p:
Solar energy has been considered a significant source of energy for many years due to the huge amounts of energy that are made freely available when modern technology is used to collect it. The planet receives a total of 4×1015m\,W\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym}
				\usepackage{amsfonts}
				\usepackage{amssymb}
				\usepackage{amsbsy}
