				\usepackage{amssymb}
				\usepackage{amsbsy}
				\usepackage{mathrsfs}
				\usepackage{upgreek}
				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document}$$\eta_{\infty }$$\end{document} must be determined. For this computational objective, the asymptotic boundary conditions at η∞\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
